About Perkins Investment Management


























CONTACT USfor Institutional InvestorsA Tradition of ValuePerkins value-oriented approach is based on the belief that investing in a diversified portfolio of high-quality, yet undervalued stocks can lead to outperformance of a benchmark over time. We believe that by conducting rigorous downside analysis before determining upside potential, we will identify companies with favorable reward-to-risk trade-offs over a full market cycle.












