Company Overview of Perkins Investment Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Perkins Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, institutions, corporations, and investment companies. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm typically invests in value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. It employs a fundamental analysis and a quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios. The firm employs in...
Perkins Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, institutions, corporations, and investment companies. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm typically invests in value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. It employs a fundamental analysis and a quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios. The firm employs in-house research to make its investments. It was founded in 1980 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with an additional office in San Francisco, California. Perkins Investment Management LLC operates as a subsidiary of Janus Capital Management LLC.
