Perkins Investment Management, LLC is an investment firm that utilizes a value-based approach in the belief that investing in a diversified portfolio of high-quality, yet undervalued stocks can lead to outperformance of a benchmark over time. It is currently located… MorePerkins Investment Management, LLC is an investment firm that utilizes a value-based approach in the belief that investing in a diversified portfolio of high-quality, yet undervalued stocks can lead to outperformance of a benchmark over time. It is currently located in Chicago, Illinois.






